From: Trip Visuals Bot <tripvisuals@railway.app>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2026 18:43:54 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] =?UTF-8?q?Fix:=20Complete=20CSP=20cleanup=20=E2=80=94?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20remove=20all=20remaining=20inline=20handlers=20and=20window?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20globals?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- admin-upload.js: Replaced inline onchange on <select> with event delegation
- admin-produtos.js: Replaced onerror attribute with img.onerror property (CSP-safe)
- catalogo.js: Full rewrite — removed 4 unnecessary window.* globals (setLayout,
  toggleSearch, fecharSearchSeVazio, filtrarProdutos), replaced both onerror
  attributes with reusable setImgFallback() helper, merged DOMContentLoaded
  handlers into single init flow
- catalogo.html: Removed onerror attribute from logo img (now set via JS)
- admin-hub.js: Removed window.setTema global + stale comment, modernized
  window.onload to addEventListener pattern
- admin-layout.js: Removed window.definirLayout global + stale comment,
  modernized window.onload to addEventListener pattern
- login.js: Removed window.fazerLogin global, cleaned up structure

Result: Zero inline event handlers, zero unnecessary window globals.
All CSP violations resolved across the entire codebase.
